<p>The <code>ajax</code> tag handles AJAX requests.</p>

<h2>Syntax</h2>
<pre>{open}ajax 'getData'{close}
  {open}!-- Returns data for AJAX call --{close}
  {open}"status": "ok", "data": [...]{close}
{open}/ajax{close}</pre>

<h2>JavaScript Integration</h2>
<pre>&lt;script&gt;
fetch('?ajax=getData')
  .then(r => r.json())
  .then(data => console.log(data));
&lt;/script&gt;

{open}ajax 'getData'{close}
  {open}"items": [1, 2, 3]{close}
{open}/ajax{close}</pre>

<h2>Note</h2>
<p>AJAX handlers return only their content, without page wrapper.</p>
